<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>세종학당 자음 학습: ㄴ, ㅁ, ㄹ</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;700&display=swap');
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }

        .canvas-container {
            position: relative;
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .stroke {
            fill: none;
            stroke-width: 25;
            stroke-linecap: round;
            stroke-linejoin: round;
            stroke-dasharray: 1000;
            stroke-dashoffset: 1000;
            transition: stroke-dashoffset 1s ease-in-out, stroke 0.3s;
        }

        .stroke-bg {
            fill: none;
            stroke: #f1f5f9;
            stroke-width: 25;
            stroke-linecap: round;
            stroke-linejoin: round;
        }

        .active .stroke {
            stroke-dashoffset: 0;
        }

        /* ㄴ (Base) - Blue */
        .color-n { stroke: #3b82f6; }
        /* ㅁ (Extension) - Green */
        .color-m-ext { stroke: #10b981; }
        /* ㄹ (Extension) - Purple */
        .color-r-ext { stroke: #a855f7; }

        .step-card {
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .step-card.active {
            border-color: #3b82f6;
            background-color: #eff6ff;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .highlight-text {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1e40af;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center py-10 px-4">

    <header class="text-center mb-10">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">한글 자음의 진화</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600">ㄴ에서 시작하여 ㅁ과 ㄹ이 완성되는 과정을 살펴보세요.</p>
    </header>

    <main class="max-w-4xl w-full flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-10 items-center justify-center">
        
        <!-- 시각화 캔버스 -->
        <div class="canvas-container flex items-center justify-center" id="mainCanvas">
            <svg width="250" height="250" viewBox="0 0 200 200" id="hangeulSvg">
                <!-- ㄴ Base Path (Common for all) -->
                <path class="stroke-bg" d="M60 40 V160 H160" />
                <path id="path-n" class="stroke color-n" d="M60 40 V160 H160" />
                
                <!-- ㅁ Extension Paths -->
                <path id="path-m-ext" class="stroke color-m-ext" d="M60 40 H160 V160" />
                
                <!-- ㄹ Extension Paths -->
                <path id="path-r-top" class="stroke color-r-ext" d="M60 40 H160 V100 H60 V160" />
            </svg>
        </div>

        <!-- 학습 단계 설명 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 w-full md:w-96">
            <!-- Step 1: ㄴ -->
            <div id="step-1" class="step-card p-5 border-2 border-transparent rounded-xl cursor-pointer bg-white shadow-sm active" onclick="showStep(1)">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                    <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold">1</span>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">ㄴ (기초, Base)</h2>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">혀가 윗잇몸에 닿는 모양입니다. 모든 자음의 바닥 지지대 역할을 합니다.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 2: ㅁ -->
            <div id="step-2" class="step-card p-5 border-2 border-transparent rounded-xl cursor-pointer bg-white shadow-sm" onclick="showStep(2)">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                    <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold">2</span>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">ㅁ (확장, Enclosure)</h2>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="highlight-text">ㄴ</span> 위에 'ㄱ' 모양을 덮어 입 모양(ㅁ)을 완성합니다. 닫힌 구조의 기초입니다.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 3: ㄹ -->
            <div id="step-3" class="step-card p-5 border-2 border-transparent rounded-xl cursor-pointer bg-white shadow-sm" onclick="showStep(3)">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                    <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-purple-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold">3</span>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">ㄹ (흐름, Flow)</h2>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="highlight-text">ㄴ</span> 위에 층을 쌓아 물 흐르듯 연결합니다. 소리가 굴러가는 역동성을 표현합니다.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <section class="mt-16 max-w-2xl text-center">
        <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-blue-100">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-blue-800 mb-2">학습 툴 설계 포인트</h3>
            <ul class="text-left text-sm text-blue-700 space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
                <li><strong>시각적 일관성:</strong> 하단의 파란색 'ㄴ'은 변하지 않고 유지되어 글자 간의 혈통을 보여줍니다.</li>
                <li><strong>레이어 시스템:</strong> 새로운 글자는 기존 뼈대 위에 추가적인 색상의 획을 얹는 방식으로 표현됩니다.</li>
                <li><strong>인지적 부담 감소:</strong> 복잡한 'ㄹ'을 'ㄴ'의 확장형으로 이해하게 하여 학습 장벽을 낮춥니다.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <script>
        function showStep(step) {
            // Reset all cards
            document.querySelectorAll('.step-card').forEach(card => card.classList.remove('active'));
            // Activate current card
            document.getElementById(`step-${step}`).classList.add('active');

            const pathN = document.getElementById('path-n');
            const pathMExt = document.getElementById('path-m-ext');
            const pathRTop = document.getElementById('path-r-top');

            // Reset strokes
            pathN.style.strokeDashoffset = "1000";
            pathMExt.style.strokeDashoffset = "1000";
            pathRTop.style.strokeDashoffset = "1000";

            // Trigger animation based on step
            setTimeout(() => {
                if (step === 1) {
                    pathN.style.strokeDashoffset = "0";
                    pathN.style.stroke = "#3b82f6";
                } else if (step === 2) {
                    pathN.style.strokeDashoffset = "0";
                    pathN.style.stroke = "#3b82f6"; // Base is blue
                    setTimeout(() => {
                        pathMExt.style.strokeDashoffset = "0";
                    }, 500);
                } else if (step === 3) {
                    pathN.style.strokeDashoffset = "0";
                    pathN.style.stroke = "#3b82f6"; // Base is blue
                    setTimeout(() => {
                        pathRTop.style.strokeDashoffset = "0";
                    }, 500);
                }
            }, 100);
        }

        // Initialize with Step 1
        window.onload = () => showStep(1);
    </script>
</body>
</html>
